
QuickSynergy 0.3.2
-----------------------------------------------------------


Installation instructions:
-----------------------------

Just follow the good old procedure:

    ./configure
    make
    make install

    
Using QuickSynergy:
-----------------------------

To start a synergy server, just enter the client machines' hostnames on
the apropriate field in the first tab of the program. Then click start.

To start a synergy client, select the Client tab on the QuickSynergy main
window and enter the server's hostname. Then click start.

Note that even if you close QuickSynergy, synergy will be kept running on the
background. If you don't want synergy to keep running after you close
QuickSynergy, then click the Stop button before closing it.
